gameDescription: The idea of the game is simply that when the game starts, the mobile is passed to every player, and all players are shown one word, except for one player who is shown something different. All players try to figure out who the spy is, and the spy tries to blend in with them and keep everyone from suspecting him.
classicModeDescription:
What appears to the spy is 
( You Are The Spy )
 which means he knows he is the spy and tries to blend in.
blindModeDescription: In this mode, what appears to the spy is a different word from the rest. This means no one knows if they are the spy or not.
noNameValidate: You can't add an empty player (:
nowYouCanAskOrVote: Now you can vote or ask again
wordRevealText:
Press Show to see the word
 and don't let anyone see it!!
